Workflow.Name: CS - case create for manual account creation for UK Partners
Workflow.Description: Sherweb's Cumulus platform currently does not support self-serve account creation for UK-based clients. This limitation creates friction in the onboarding process, especially for prospects who expect a seamless digital experience. To bridge this gap temporarily, UK clients are asked to fill out a Microsoft Form to initiate account creation manually. However, the current manual process lacks automation, traceability, and consistency, leading to delays and potential errors in account setup and billing coordination. This flow's purpose is to facilitate all that while keeping a good track record of what's happening.

Relevant Information
